dc_title_s: Parks and Cemeteries: Ciudad Juarez, Mexico, 2010
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents parks and cemeteries in Ciudad Juarez (Mexico). LeadDog Consulting (Originator and Publisher) has a Mexico-based data partner network for which they have access to GIS data sets to create city streets maps for Mexico, which may include streets, street names, street classifications, points of interests, landuse, water, neighborhood points, and railroads. These data are intended for geographic display and analysis at the city level. No responsibility is assumed by LeadDog Consulting. Instituto Nacional de Estadística, Geografía e Informática (Mexico) and LeadDog Consulting. (2010). Parks and Cemeteries: Ciudad Juarez, Mexico, 2010. LeadDog Consulting. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/pr606gm7193. This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
